# Display Language: English Only

**项目所有面向用户的显示信息必须使用英语。**

All user-facing display text in this project must be in **English**.

## Scope

- **SilentPassUI** (React/TypeScript)
- **Android** (Kotlin/Compose)
- **bizSite** (React/TypeScript)
- **Any other UI surface** in the project

## What Must Be English

- Labels, buttons, placeholders, hints
- Error messages, toast content, AlertDialog text
- Init/read/topup/payment status messages
- API error messages shown to users
- Any string displayed to end users

## Do Not

- Use Chinese or other non-English languages for UI display
- Add new user-facing strings in languages other than English

Code comments (e.g. `//`, `/**`) may remain in any language for developer convenience.
